# Confluxe Deployment Context

## Hosting
- **Platform:** Vercel
- **Production:** www.confluxe.in (main branch)
- **Staging:** staging.confluxe.in (preview branch)
- **DNS:** GoDaddy (confluxe.in)

## Git Workflow
- **main** → deploys to www.confluxe.in
- **preview** → deploys to staging.confluxe.in (client approval before production)

## Scripts
- `scripts/push-to-github.ps1` - Pushes main and preview branches to GitHub
- See `SETUP-GITHUB.md` for one-time GitHub repo setup
